HEADWORD: Suant
<hw>Su"ant</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Cf. <er>Sue</er> to
pursue.]</ety> <def>Spread equally over the surface; uniform;
even.</def> <altsp>[Written also <asp>suent</asp>.]</altsp>
